original_title: Daisy Derkins vs. The Bloodthirsty Beast of Barren Pines!
overview: Monster-slaying hero Daisy Derkins ventures into the woods to deal with a carnivorous dinosaur, and along the way runs afoul of a touring punk band, a manic bounty hunter, a trio of voluptuous female criminals, and a family of mutant cannibals.
title: Daisy Derkins vs. The Bloodthirsty Beast of Barren Pines!
